quote: This Morty made the mistake of looking into a mirror while touching the supercooled outer casing of the Morty Multiplication Generator that his Rick created.

title: Greaser Morty (Pocket Mortys)
quote: This Morty was the leader of the pack, rebelling against whatever you've got. He lost everything in a grease fire and had to sell his bike to keep himself in leathers.

title: Multi Morty
quote: This Morty was caught in the shockwave caused by the last 2 Mortys interference with the Morty Multiplication generator and is forever stuck in a 5 dimensional Morty Multiplication feedback loop.

title: Double Morty (Pocket Mortys)
quote: This Morty made the mistake of holding a penny while standing too close to the bio-magnetic field of the Morty Multiplication Generator that his Rick created.

title: Phantom Morty
quote: This Morty will visit you at 2 am in the morning if you leave this game running in front of a mirror in an empty room. Knock the door 3 times before going to sleep.

title: Ghostly Morty (Pocket Mortys)
quote: This Morty floats over freshly dug graves and can be seen in south facing mirrors on full moon nights during the month of October.

title: Spooky Morty
quote: This Morty hides in the cupboards of empty rooms and cuts holes in the family bed sheets. He is cold to the touch and can never return home again.

title: Orange Shirt Morty
quote: This Morty's shirt makes him look like a carrot to any rabbits that might be watching from nearby forests. Y'know, like rabbits do.

title: Red Shirt Morty
quote: This Morty finds the color red powerful, just like the blood that runs through the veins of all Morty's who follow the "True Way of the Heart" on the path to their bliss.

title: Blue Shirt Morty
quote: This Morty does not want to be defined by wearing the same yellow shirt every day, as other Mortys do. He opted for blue, the color of the summer sky and the distant seas.

title: Pocket Mortys Morty
quote: This Morty feels a bit of self promotion could go a long way. He wants to share his love of this game with his friends.

title: Jerry's Game Morty
quote: This Morty is not ashamed to promote other Rick and Morty games. Y'know, like Jerry's Game. You should download Jerry's Game, by the way.

title: Ad Space Morty (Pocket Mortys)
quote: This Morty is working for free for Jerry. He hopes to never see another apple in his life.

title: Hipster Morty
quote: This Morty doesn't care what you think of him. He already knows he's got swag.

title: Beard Morty (Pocket Mortys)
quote: This Morty works in a very trendy part of town. On Fridays, he enjoys a nice burrito.

title: Mustache Morty
quote: This Morty will take any opportunity to display his fine facial hair, and has even won trophies for it.

title: No Mercy Morty
quote: This Morty has been corrupted by the power he feels in his arms and legs, he will show you no mercy if you do not follow the way of the fist. There is no fear in his Dojo or his heart.

title: Karate Morty
quote: This Morty is a dedicated practitioner of karate spending 12 hours a day working on his forms, sparring, and strength training. This Morty loves karate more than life.

title: Self Defense Morty
quote: This Morty used to get beaten up every day on his way to school. He decided to take self-defense classes to boost his confidence and physical strength.

title: Test X72 Morty
quote: This Morty is the result of a transdimensional pharmaceutical conglomerate's further experimentation on a patented genome acquired through a hostile takeover

title: Test X46 Morty
quote: This Morty was the second successful result in a series of experiments that led to the downfall and financial ruin of his creator. This Morty can only feel pain and hunger

title: Test X1 Morty
quote: This Morty was the first result in a series of experiments performed by a guilt-ridden Rick who spent his dying days trying to bring back his lost grandson.

title: Three Eye Morty
quote: This Morty has seen everything but has yet to feel the warmth of a loving touch.

title: One Eye Morty
quote: This Morty has never felt accepted among the other Mortys. He hopes that they will one day see things the way he does.

title: No Eye Morty
quote: This Morty refuses to talk about his impairment, but some say he lost his eyes when his Rick tried to swap them out for his own.

title: Evil Rabbit Morty
quote: This Morty is an evil cosplayer from a dimension where Halloween is 340 days long. His rabbit costume used to be pink and cute, but has since faded to a dull gray from overuse.

title: Ancient Morty
quote: This Morty chose poorly. Dried up and dead to the world, only hatred, cruel fate, and years of modern food preservatives keep his wicked heart beating.
Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade

title: Rabbit Morty
quote: This Morty was bitten by a radioactive bunny, and now turns into a rabbit every time a carrot is near. Unfortunately, he is from a dimension where humans evolved from carrots.

title: Geriatric Morty
quote: This Morty sits alone in his small room, looking through old photo albums at faces he can't quite remember. He waits for the comfort only the grave can bring.

title: Old Morty
quote: This Morty remembers when this all used to be fields and he could fly his kite freely without the fear of it becoming stuck in a tree.

title: Hobo Morty
quote: This Morty Lurks around inner city parks waiting to touch unsupervised dogs without the owners consent.

title: Unkempt Morty
quote: This Morty refuses to take a bath or brush his teeth. He also appreciates the health benefits of garlic.

morty_page.title: Scruffy Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has never much cared for his appearance.

morty_page.title: Exo-Prime Morty
morty_page.quote: After evolving further this intergalactic Morty soon became the fearsome tyrant of his dimension. Having nightly rendezvous with the local ladies.

morty_page.title: Spork Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty decided to combine his fork, and spoon with his Ricks Combo-Ray.

morty_page.title: Off The Grid Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty spends most of his time tied to a tree. He believes the leaves will cleanse the mistakes of his past.

morty_page.title: Exo-Omega Morty
morty_page.quote: This mutated Morty has earned the respect of his peers, and is learning to lead a normal life.

morty_page.title: Peace Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty hopes to spread love throughout the world. He buys all his clothes from thrift shops.

morty_page.title: Hippie Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty makes his own tie-dyed T-shirts and sells them at the local park.

morty_page.title: Fork Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty got tired of his beloved spoon.

morty_page.title: Spoon Morty
morty_page.quote: This Mortys only friend is his spoon.

morty_page.title: Green Shirt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty wears a shirt of the purest green that ever was seen in many a year around these parts, here to behold in all its glory!

morty_page.title: Exo-Alpha Morty
morty_page.quote: This mutated Morty is a nobody in his dimension. He lives in the sewers, and has tea parties with rats.

morty_page.title: Rainbow Shirt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is the 1 of 2 where neither friends nor loving family may go, his eyes watching a thousand suns and a thousand moons rise and fall together a thousand times.

morty_page.title: Purple Shirt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty wears a purple shirt he was given when he attended a seminar on 'power dressing' a few months before the release of this game.

morty_page.title: Orange Shirt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty's shirt makes him look like a carrot to any rabbits that might be watching from nearby forests. Y'know, like rabbits do.

morty_page.title: Red Shirt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty finds the color red powerful, just like the blood that runs through the veins of all Morty's who follow the "True Way of the Heart" on the path to their bliss.

morty_page.title: Triple Snoozle Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where Earth developed as the fourth planet from the sun after Theia settled in a stable orbit.

morty_page.title: Tank Top Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty works out once a week and likes to show off. He has yet to discover deodorant.

morty_page.title: Wild Man Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty lurks in the trees to hide from trainers, but will attack if they enter his territory. The distant memories of his previous life fade a little more each day...

morty_page.title: Survivalist Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty adapted to the harsh conditions after the Mortyland Uprising, scavenging anything he could use to keep himself alive.

morty_page.title: Survivor Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty survived the original Mortyland Uprising by hiding under a pile of soiled merchandise in a gift shop. He remembers the happier times.

morty_page.title: Ace Pilot Morty
morty_page.quote: This ol’ Morty can’t be beat in the skys. Even when drawing crabs this old chap can be seen zigzagging around every archie and never pipped, not even once what what!

morty_page.title: Prancer Morty
morty_page.quote: This mythical Morty appears every time a tear drop reaches the ocean. He is said to shimmer like the moonlight reflected in a still pool.

morty_page.title: Volcan Morty
morty_page.quote: This mythical Morty is said to appear near the homes of the recently deceased and can only be seen by labradors and people with peanut allergies.

morty_page.title: Birdosaur Morty
morty_page.quote: This mythical Morty can be found nesting in the Mortian Forest near Morty City. His tail feathers are said to smell like teenage shame.

morty_page.title: Violent Morty
morty_page.quote: There is Morty, that is him, and his old man, that is Rick and the two would traverse the ol' interdimensionals together until alas brothers, a mishap put a right end to all that tomfoolery.

morty_page.title: Dangerous Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty runs a small business and spends most of his time traveling the country. The way he sees it, only through total failure lies the true path to success.

morty_page.title: Loner Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty spends his days in his small dirty apartment training for that one big moment to put the world right. He enjoys going to the cinema by himself.

morty_page.title: Rainbow Suit Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty wants to be a rainbow and can be seen standing on the edge of high buildings after the rain.

morty_page.title: Motion Capture Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty uses his whole body to help large game studios create animations for match 3 games.

morty_page.title: Skin Suit Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty enjoys wandering the local park naked but didn’t want the coming winter to effect his lifestyle choice.

morty_page.title: Head Chef Morty
morty_page.quote: This successful Morty lent his name to an animation studio, only to be horrified by the content they produce.

morty_page.title: Pastry Chef Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty’s intense chef training has left him unable to speak. He can only express his emotions through interpretive baking.

morty_page.title: Kitchen Boy Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is responsible for washing dishes, taking out the trash, and changing the fryer grease. He smells like french fries and sweat.

morty_page.title: Poorly Cloned Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was found by Beth and Jerry among the possessions of their deceased Rick. Unable to find the right words, they decided to raise him as Morty's twin.

morty_page.title: Hardboiled Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is getting too old for this. It's his last day on the job, he’s past the point of no return, and he won't stop until his target is behind bars.
morty_page.characteristics: Loose Cannon, Doesn't Play by the Rules

morty_page.title: Detective Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty’s peptic ulcer burns from all those coffee-soaked nights spent investigating a quintuple Mortycide that still haunts his every waking hour.

morty_page.title: Rookie Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty’s first day on the beat has been complicated. His fellow Cop Mortys questioned his loyalty after opting out of the protection racket run by the precinct’s Rick.

morty_page.title: Seedling Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty grows out of the ground below the recently hanged and is said to induce madness in anyone who licks him. His scream can only be heard by unsuspecting dogs.

morty_page.title: Fawn Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty spends all his time standing in the forest clearing by the light of the full moon, waiting for the chance to see his mother's shade pass by through the trees.

morty_page.title: Triple Denim Morty
morty_page.quote: Two's a company, three's a crowd. This Morty likes denim three times more than a regular Morty.

morty_page.title: Double Denim Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty dares, dares to double... the denim.

morty_page.title: Denim Shorts Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty likes short shorts. So much so that he never takes them off, even in the shower.

morty_page.title: Cup Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has a terrible secret and would be devastated if anyone ever found out.

morty_page.title: Old One Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is the oldest and most highly ranked of all Morty vampires. Despite this, the other vampires joke that his ears allow interdimensional hearing even though he is completely deaf.

morty_page.title: Count Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty gave up drinking human blood in the late 50s and is now a children's entertainer/scarer.

morty_page.title: New Blood Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty read too many teenage novels and believed that becoming a vampire would make him more attractive to the opposite sex. Everyone he loved died long ago.

morty_page.title: Miami Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty sleeps on the beach during the day and works as a dancer in a famous 80s night club. His signature dance move is The Lollipop.

morty_page.title: Cap'n Morty
morty_page.quote: This notorious Morty is the captain of a large vessel named Jessica's Pearl and once traded his eye for a barrel of gun powder infused rum.

morty_page.title: Swashbuckle Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty once found a treasure chest of gold in the Caribbean but was tricked into trading it for a date with mermaid, who turned out to be a reverse mermaid.

morty_page.title: Cabin Boy Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is the son of the famous pirate 'Titanic Jerry', who was responsible for one of the worst pirate ship incidents in recorded history. Cabin Boy Morty is not trusted to be lookout.

morty_page.title: Rick Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was tired of always being told he was an idiot and would never have even half the brain power that his Rick possessed.

morty_page.title: Beth Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty never recovered from his mother leaving the family when he was young. He decided to do the only thing in his power to bring her back.

morty_page.title: Summer Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty discovered that his Rick erased all his memories of having an older sister to “keep him from pain”. He now tries to keep her alive in his heart.

morty_page.title: Sexy Devil Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has been wearing the same cheap, ill-fitting devil costume since last halloween.

morty_page.title: Exoskeleton Morty
morty_page.quote: TThis Morty spends his days hoping his dog doesn’t realize he's human. His favorite food is marrowbone jelly.

morty_page.title: Jerry Fan Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has spent most of his life in the Jerry World theme park. He was raised by the Jerrys that work there after being accidentally abandoned by his Rick.

morty_page.title: Jerry Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty had a difficult life growing up and never knew his real father until he discovered an old photo album hidden among his mother's posessions.

morty_page.title: Turbulent Juice Morty
morty_page.quote: In a world where muscular Mortys are coming, and they're coming strong, no Morty is safe from the power of Turbulent Juice Morty. 'Cuz he's gonna take CARE of it.

morty_page.title: Headism Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty loves the giant head in the sky. Look, see? He’s wearing the hat and everything.

morty_page.title: Renegade Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has gone Morty-crazy from years of pointless fighting in the Grand Inter-dimensional Morty War. He witnessed many terrible things during this time.

morty_page.title: Shell Shocked Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension locked deep within the Grand Inter-dimensional Morty War. He’s having a hard time forgiving himself for the things he was ordered to do to his fellow Mortys.

morty_page.title: Boot Camp Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from one in a string of related dimension where all Ricks are required to submit their Mortys to fight in Grand Inter-dimensional Morty War.

morty_page.title: Werewolf Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is cursed to spend his final days as a werewolf, tormented by the terrible things he has done. But hey, on the plus side, he does have a beautiful, shiny coat.

morty_page.title: Dog Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has the appearance of a dog and spends his evenings howling at the moon and... well, being a dog.

morty_page.title: Dog Bite Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was bitten by a small dog while on a backpacking trip.

morty_page.title: Raptor Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty’s Rick had a crazy idea to start a theme park inhabited solely by human-dino hybrids. He ended up financially and emotionally ruined due to lack of interest.

morty_page.title: Reptile Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has cold blood, saving his Rick 38% in heating costs per year.

morty_page.title: Boulder Morty
morty_page.quote: Rick found this Morty partially lodged inside of his experimental Medusa Device.

morty_page.title: Petrified Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was fully aware of the risks involved from excessive skin contact with Rick’s Medusa Device but decided the benefits outweighed the negative effects.

morty_page.title: Stoned Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty unfortunately mistook his Rick’s "Medusa Device" for a novelty item and was unaware of the side effects from excessive skin contact.

morty_page.title: Banana Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has committed several unspeakable crimes while dressed as a banana. No one has seen or heard from his Rick in three years.

morty_page.title: Orange Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty broke away from his tour group and sampled some experimental orange candy from the off-limits research lab of his Rick’s factory complex.

morty_page.title: Strawberry Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was framed by his Rick for multi-dimensional omnicide and has since built a new life for himself by hiding among the strawberry people of Fragaria-Prime.

morty_page.title: Host Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty smells like sour milk and emits deadly spores every evening, just before sunset. There is nothing left of who he used to be.

morty_page.title: Parasitic Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty surprised his family by turning up at home one day after his funeral. Unsure of the best course of action, his family kept him chained up in the back yard.

morty_page.title: Infected Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty hasn’t felt right since using the public restroom of a re-fermented burger joint on a small planetoid in the inner asteroid belt of the Epsilon Eridani system.

morty_page.title: Goo Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is made of goo and smells like warm saline solution, body spray and shame.

morty_page.title: Jelly Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty's heart dissolved long ago into the clear, pink jelly that makes up his current form. He stains anything he touches.

morty_page.title: Blob Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where all the cells in his body have merged into one. He is soft and sticky to the touch and warm inside.

morty_page.title: Super Rick Fan Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is a big fan of Grandpa Rick and is a fully paid member of the Rick Fan Club - a scam run by a desperate Rick who needs the money.

morty_page.title: Super Morty Fan Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty loves Mortys so much that his family had to stage an intervention to discuss his narcissistic addiction.

morty_page.title: Double Snoozle Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where the early planetoid Theia crashed into Venus instead of what would have later become Earth.

morty_page.title: Single Snoozle Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where Venus never formed, making Earth the second planet from the sun.

morty_page.title: Black Hole Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is full of wonders that are waiting just beyond his event horizon to be exposed from the darkness that hides them...

morty_page.title: Sun Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has a small role as the Sun in a local amateur drama production. It would mean the world to him if his Rick could attend on opening night. His Rick is planning to stay at home.

morty_page.title: Moon Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty worships the Moon and is planning a fantastical expedition to find the hidden gallery-tomb and the portrait it contains that will confirm his beliefs. His Rick has refused to help.

morty_page.title: Super Unicorn Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty took the full force of a rainbow laser blast to the heart from a Rick who was jealous of his beauty. Healed by the Unicorns of Crystal Forest, he now possesses their powers.

morty_page.title: Unicorn Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is a beautiful and majestic unicorn and would prefer to be known by his unicorn name, 'Stardust Harmony'.

morty_page.title: Mushroom Pizza Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where all life is comprised of living slices of pizza. Mushrooms are the latest fashion trend.

morty_page.title: Pizza Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where all life is comprised of living slices of pizza.

morty_page.title: Unicorn Chaser Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty believes in unicorns and will one day find a unicorn to call his own. Only then will his nightmares stop.

morty_page.title: Big Tongue Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty never fully recovered from the nuclear waste his Rick tried to feed him. His tongue will make your skin tingle if it touches you.

morty_page.title: Punk Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has had enough of society's rules and will no longer take the weight of The Man pushing him down.

morty_page.title: Pepperoni Pizza Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where all life is comprised of living slices of pizza. He has recently contracted a nasty case of pepperoni after sharing an unprotected oven.

morty_page.title: Butterfly Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty failed to become a beautiful butterfly. In fact, he has lost most of his motor skills and can no longer communicate.

morty_page.title: Cocoon Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is covered in a hard, silk shell. When he emerges, he hopes to be a beautiful butterfly.

morty_page.title: Diamond Eyes Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty tried having his eyes "shined" to allow him to see in the dark. It didn't work so his Rick just replaced his eyes with diamonds.

morty_page.title: Mutant Flu Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty became terribly ill after Jerry tried to make dinner for him. Jerry used one of Rick's inventions to teleport him away so no one would find out.

morty_page.title: Flu Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where they haven't invented vaccines. This Morty is meant to return home with a cure for the common cold.

morty_page.title: Cold Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is always too cold. He likes warm cups of cocoa and appreciates a comforter with a tog rating of at least 13.5.

morty_page.title: Flaming Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was exposed to a large dose of cosmic radiation after his Rick abandoned him in deep space.

morty_page.title: Hot Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is always too warm. He likes strawberry ice cream and a cool summer breeze.

morty_page.title: Asleep Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is under a witch's spell-- one that can only be broken by a kiss from a handsome prince.

morty_page.title: Frozen Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty had a terrible accident in a cryogenics lab while trying to save his Rick from a life-threatening disease.

morty_page.title: Sleepy Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is lucky to get even two hours of sleep at night. He suffers from night terrors that developed after he saw his own Rick get turned inside out.

morty_page.title: Tired Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has missed a lot of school thanks to his Rick's crazy adventures. He is now looking at a C- in Math.

morty_page.title: Chops Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty is a fan of 80's cop dramas. He hopes to one day find a dimension where crime doesn't pay.

morty_page.title: Mullet Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was the first in his dimension to grow a mullet. He was quickly banished to another dimension and told not to return.

morty_page.title: Tank Top Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty works out once a week and likes to show off. He has yet to discover deodorant.

morty_page.title: V Neck Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty likes to wear low-cut tops. He feels that his v-neck gives him an air of superiority over other Mortys.

morty_page.title: Afro Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty spends most of his day tending to his hair. He is fully aware that it's the only thing he has going for him.

morty_page.title: Egg Morty
morty_page.quote: This egg appears to contain a life force.

morty_page.title: Mascot Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty can often be seen hyping up the crowd.

morty_page.title: Cronenberg Morty
morty_page.quote: This article is about Cronenberg Morty. You may be looking for

morty_page.title: Guard Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty lives a life of strict rules and 5:00am wake-up calls. He dreams of one day leaving this life behind and living in the country with a cow named Daisy.

morty_page.title: Hammerhead Morty
morty_page.quote: I'm more than just a hammer!

morty_page.title: Robot Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty claims he is a real boy. It is unknown if his software has malfunctioned or if he really does contain the mind of an actual, biological Morty.

morty_page.title: Cowboy Morty
morty_page.quote: This article is about Cowboy Morty. You may be looking for

morty_page.title: Mini Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty comes from a tiny world created by another Rick. His tiny world was destroyed when that Rick mistook it for a pizza slice. This Morty wants vengeance for the loss of his people.

morty_page.title: Cyclops Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was extradited from his home world after he caused a nuclear silo to explode.

morty_page.title: Aqua Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty comes from a family of fish people. He is a vegan but enjoys chicken on Fridays.

morty_page.title: Shadow Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has lost his true form. He wanders around aimlessly in search of himself, unaware that his body was buried many years ago.

morty_page.title: Sausage Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty fell into a meat processing machine during a field trip to the sausage factory. He hasn't felt the same since then.

morty_page.title: Gaseous Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is from a dimension where it's possible to have really, REALLY bad gas.

morty_page.title: Business Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty is never late for a meeting but has never made it home in time for his son's birthday party. He's hoping for a promotion.

morty_page.title: Reverse Mermaid Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is an experiment gone wrong. His Rick was driven mad by the allure of mythical Mermaid Morty and wanted his own.

morty_page.title: Mermaid Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is sometimes thought to be a myth. He sits on rocks and lures fishermen to their doom.

morty_page.title: Swimmer Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty feels more at home in the water. He can hold his breath underwater for 3 minutes and 37 seconds.

morty_page.title: Psychokinetic Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty has been seen moving whole planets with his mind. He can also make a cheese sandwich without touching the bread.

morty_page.title: Telekinetic Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was expelled from school when he accidentally crushed his teacher after concentrating on a math problem too hard.

morty_page.title: Telepathic Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty woke up with a bad headache and a scar on his head. He is convinced he saw Rick leaving his room.

morty_page.title: Wizard Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty enjoys role playing. He uses it as an escape from the real world where he can be a powerful wizard and rule entire lands.

morty_page.title: Mystic Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty claims he can read minds. He says he uncovered his Rick's dark secrets and turned him in to the Council of Ricks.

morty_page.title: Magic Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is deceitful. He lied on his exam paper and said he finished his vegetables when he actually did not.

morty_page.title: Veiny Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty asked his Rick for help in his biology class. He's regretted it ever since.

morty_page.title: Wrestler Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty can cut a promo like the best of them. But he was forced to retire after a botched suplex from the top rop broke his neck.

morty_page.title: Skeleton Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty asked his Rick to help him with his Halloween costume. He's regretted it ever since.

morty_page.title: No Skin Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty asked his Rick to create a powerful spot removal cream for his acne but has regretted it ever since.

morty_page.title: Buff Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty doesn't know when enough is enough. He plays ruff and wont take no for an answer.

morty_page.title: Crazy Cat Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has found friendship in his feline companions. He now struggles to socialise with humans.

morty_page.title: Two Cat Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has adopted two cats. He is unaware that they are actually alien parasites trying to control his mind
morty_page.characteristics: Can hold 2 cats at a time

morty_page.title: Stray Cat Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty believes his Rick is trapped inside the mind of a cat. (His Rick is actually winning an inter-dimensional game of hide and seek.)

morty_page.title: Biker Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty was born to be wild, a son of the open road, a life of hard living and a hard women with his back to the wind and grit in his teeth, forever riding into the desert sun.

morty_page.title: Greaser Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty was the leader of the pack, rebelling against whatever you've got. He lost everything in a grease fire and had to sell his bike to keep himself in leathers.

morty_page.title: Multi Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was caught in the shockwave caused by the last 2 Mortys interference with the Morty Multiplication generator and is forever stuck in a 5 dimensional Morty Multiplication feedback loop.

morty_page.title: Triple Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty made the mistake of looking into a mirror while touching the supercooled outer casing of the Morty Multiplication Generator that his Rick created.

morty_page.title: Double Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty made the mistake of holding a penny while standing too close to the bio-magnetic field of the Morty Multiplication Generator that his Rick created.

morty_page.title: Phantom Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty will visit you at 2 am in the morning if you leave this game running in front of a mirror in an empty room. Knock the door 3 times before going to sleep.

morty_page.title: Ghostly Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty floats over freshly dug graves and can be seen in south facing mirrors on full moon nights during the month of October.

morty_page.title: Spooky Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty hides in the cupboards of empty rooms and cuts holes in the family bed sheets. He is cold to the touch and can never return home again.

morty_page.title: Jerry's Game Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is not ashamed to promote other Rick and Morty games. Y'know, like Jerry's Game. You should download Jerry's Game, by the way.

morty_page.title: Colossal Head Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty regrets playing in toxic waste. His Rick has since disowned him and doesn't even write him letters anymore.

morty_page.title: Giant Head Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has lost all sense of smell and feels no pain. His medical condition is not recognized amongst Ricks.

morty_page.title: Ad Space Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty is working for free for Jerry. He hopes to never see another apple in his life.

morty_page.title: Hipster Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty doesn't care what you think of him. He already knows he's got swag.

morty_page.title: Beard Morty (Pocket Mortys)
morty_page.quote: This Morty works in a very trendy part of town. On Fridays, he enjoys a nice burrito.

morty_page.title: Blue Shirt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty does not want to be defined by wearing the same yellow shirt every day, as other Mortys do. He opted for blue, the color of the summer sky and the distant seas.

morty_page.title: Pocket Mortys Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty feels a bit of self promotion could go a long way. He wants to share his love of this game with his friends.

morty_page.title: Mustache Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty will take any opportunity to display his fine facial hair, and has even won trophies for it.

morty_page.title: No Mercy Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has been corrupted by the power he feels in his arms and legs, he will show you no mercy if you do not follow the way of the fist. There is no fear in his Dojo or his heart.

morty_page.title: Karate Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is a dedicated practitioner of karate spending 12 hours a day working on his forms, sparring, and strength training. This Morty loves karate more than life.

morty_page.title: Self Defense Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty used to get beaten up every day on his way to school. He decided to take self-defense classes to boost his confidence and physical strength.

morty_page.title: Test X72 Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is the result of a transdimensional pharmaceutical conglomerate's further experimentation on a patented genome acquired through a hostile takeover

morty_page.title: Test X46 Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was the second successful result in a series of experiments that led to the downfall and financial ruin of his creator. This Morty can only feel pain and hunger

morty_page.title: Test X1 Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was the first result in a series of experiments performed by a guilt-ridden Rick who spent his dying days trying to bring back his lost grandson.

morty_page.title: Three Eye Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has seen everything but has yet to feel the warmth of a loving touch.

morty_page.title: One Eye Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty has never felt accepted among the other Mortys. He hopes that they will one day see things the way he does.

morty_page.title: No Eye Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty refuses to talk about his impairment, but some say he lost his eyes when his Rick tried to swap them out for his own.

morty_page.title: Evil Rabbit Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty is an evil cosplayer from a dimension where Halloween is 340 days long. His rabbit costume used to be pink and cute, but has since faded to a dull gray from overuse.

morty_page.title: Ancient Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty chose poorly. Dried up and dead to the world, only hatred, cruel fate, and years of modern food preservatives keep his wicked heart beating.

morty_page.title: Geriatric Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty sits alone in his small room, looking through old photo albums at faces he can't quite remember. He waits for the comfort only the grave can bring.

morty_page.title: Old Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty remembers when this all used to be fields and he could fly his kite freely without the fear of it becoming stuck in a tree.

morty_page.title: Hobo Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty Lurks around inner city parks waiting to touch unsupervised dogs without the owners consent.

morty_page.title: Rabbit Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty was bitten by a radioactive bunny, and now turns into a rabbit every time a carrot is near. Unfortunately, he is from a dimension where humans evolved from carrots.

morty_page.title: Unkempt Morty
morty_page.quote: This Morty refuses to take a bath or brush his teeth. He also appreciates the health benefits of garlic.
